{"tid":1934673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Bonnie?]渣打荃灣眾安街分行有員工初步確診新型肺炎　暫關分行","createTime":"2020-03-20T05:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T07:38:15.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc985fd941a792e2ffb1ff57e8a20e999e5a58a2","tid":1934673,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"渣打香港表示，今早接獲一名員工通知初步確診感染新型冠狀病毒。該員工於荃灣眾安街分行工作，目前正接受治療。有關員工於周末出席一項私人聚會，有出席該聚會的人士，其後證實確診感染新型冠狀病毒。該員工3月16日休假，3月17日回分行工作，翌日不適留家休息，求醫後今早初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n有關分行的員工即日起自行隔離14日，銀行亦正聯繫與該員工有密切接觸的客人，提醒他們採取預防性安全措施。該分行會徹底清潔消毒，並會暫時關閉直至另行通知。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515753-20200320.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515753-20200320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=6e59d796\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515753-20200320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6cd9e3d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515753-20200320.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0615b4ce7cbea298112b33860bc35c4760110adb","tid":1934673,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T05:50:41.000Z","msg":"都叫咗呢期唔好聚會<br />\n聚少陣會死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84211a6c94991e0aca3baa81584b1350d23ce25d","tid":1934673,"uid":164198,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:27:11.000Z","msg":"今日碓診又增加,<br />\n依排大家都係少d gathering"},{"pid":"9055b7697a5b5a43250b84b1166f897942322c8a","tid":1934673,"uid":146241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"參加婚禮？"},{"pid":"ce6ba8c4a6073c362f5eb56142380b65046576f8","tid":1934673,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0615b4ce7cbea298112b33860bc35c4760110adb",